[Tepat.]

00:36:42.600 --> 00:36:43.880
Ibuku ada di sini.

00:36:43.920 --> 00:36:44.960
Jika saya pergi ke Hong Kong,

00:36:44.960 --> 00:36:45.680
Bagaimana dengan dia?

00:36:45.680 --> 00:36:47.760
Ibumu? Dia punya Fu.

